                <h1>Understanding Background Questionnaires for Hiring Success</h1>
                <p>A background questionnaire is a tool used to gather detailed information about an individual's personal, educational, and professional history. It aims to assess a candidate's suitability for a role, ensuring they have the necessary qualifications and background. This process enhances hiring decisions by verifying information and uncovering potential red flags.</p>
